NO MORE EXCUSES 2017 (Day 25)
I really need to exercise more. Compared with my past pictures, I can clearly see that I am not my best shape. Also, the incredibly humid weather has made it impossible to do my workout. My home does not have air conditioning so when the weather is hot, it's really bad. Not that I'm trying to make excuses but in this heat, each time you try to move you are only able to very sluggishly.

Nonetheless, I am so glad that I was able to squeeze in my workout tonight. Sending you all much love from Marikina. God bless us all!
